description.en:
Saitoki Inu launched on 2/8/22 on the ETH network by an experienced team . 




Saitama and Floki, already both legendary, come together to form the greatest token of all time. 






We have a fully developed P2E game ready for release.






the P2E is is an open economy that enables people to earn real money from playing games a gaming environment using our token. 











We offer equity to players where they can earn and also collaborate with developers to make vital contributions to the game.
